    "timestamp": "2026-07-11T17:40:18.653817+00:00",
    "instance_id": 1,
    "name": "ceshi",
    "symbol": "ETH-USDT-SWAP",
    "type": "pnl_calculation_bug",
    "root_cause": "PnlAccountingEngine.recompute 使用 _compute_pnl_metrics 计算 unrealized_pnl = total_pnl - realized_pnl，其中 total_pnl = sell_total - buy_total - fee。当仅有买单（无卖单）时，unrealized_pnl = -buy_total - fee，即将全部买入成本视为未实现亏损，严重失真。策略#1 仅1笔买单成交(1819.0×10合约)，unrealized_pnl 错误显示为 -1818.6362。",
    "fix": "在 recompute 中改用 (current_price - avg_buy_price) * net_position - 预估手续费 计算 unrealized_pnl，与 incremental_update / heartbeat_snapshot 保持一致。修复后 recompute 结果：unrealized=4.1650。",
    "file_modified": "backend/services/pnl_accounting_engine.py (recompute 方法, 行 96-135)",
    "old_value": {
      "unrealized_pnl": -1818.6362,
      "total_pnl": -1818.6362
    },
    "new_value": {
      "unrealized_pnl": 4.165,
      "total_pnl": 4.165
    }
  },
  {
    "timestamp": "2026-07-11T17:40:18.653833+00:00",
    "instance_id": 3,
    "name": "research_grid20_07111730",
    "symbol": "ETH-USDT-SWAP",
    "type": "reconcile_unit_mismatch_bug",
    "root_cause": "reconcile_positions 中 real_total 直接使用 OKX API 返回的 pos（合约张数），而 virtual_total 来自 PnlRecord.net_position（币种数量 = actual_qty = sz × ctVal）。ETH-USDT-SWAP ctVal=0.1，策略#3 卖1合约：virtual=-0.1 ETH，real=-1 张，diff=0.9 实为单位不一致导致，非真实仓位偏差。",
    "fix": "在 reconcile_positions 中通过 instrument_cache 获取 ctVal，将 real_total 乘以 ctVal 转换为币种数量。修复后：virtual=0, real=0, matched=True。",
    "file_modified": "backend/services/pnl_accounting_engine.py (reconcile_positions 方法, 行 597-609)",
    "old_value": {
      "virtual_total": -0.1,
      "real_total": -1.0,
      "diff": 0.9,
      "matched": false
    },
    "new_value": {
      "virtual_total": 0.0,
      "real_total": 0.0,
      "diff": 0.0,
      "matched": true
    }
  },
